com.im.njams.sdk.model

Class ProcessModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.im.njams.sdk.model.ProcessModel

  • public class ProcessModel
extends Object
    A ProcessModel represents one process/flow in engine to monitor. Instances of running jobs for the process are managed here.
    Author:
    pnientiedt
